Long-term, Northstar should become a connected information system.

```
                    User
                      │
     ┌────────────────┼────────────────┐
     │                │                │
  Missions        Projects       Knowledge
     │                │                │
     │                │                │
  Progress         Assets           Notes
     │                │                │
     └────────────────┼────────────────┘
